---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Financing your CORELOT home"
  description="Construction-perm loan guidance, budget ranges, and lender conversations tailored to CORELOT and WL Martin Homes plans."
  canonicalPath="/financing"
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <p class="pill">Financing</p>
    <h1>Plan ahead with construction-perm clarity.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Use these steps to set realistic allowances, lock in rate protections, and coordinate land improvements.</p>
  </header>

  <ol class="steps">
    <li>
      <h2>Budget framing</h2>
      <p>Align plan choice, structural options, and site prep allowances before you speak with a lender.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h2>Lender introductions</h2>
      <p>We share trusted construction-perm partners who understand WL Martin Homes plans and CORELOT schedules.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h2>Lock it in</h2>
      <p>Confirm draw schedules, contingency allowances, and inspection milestones so every party stays coordinated.</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p>Ready to review your options? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> for a personalized walkthrough.</p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-header { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.lede { color: #4b5563; }
.steps {
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.steps h2 { margin: 0.1rem 0; }
</style>
